    "asOf": "2019-05-23",
    "date": "2021-01-19T18:27:00Z",
    "text": "Labor, Human, and Civil Rights Trade Policy Act\n\nThis bill requires trade agreement implementing bills to (1) adhere to certain labor standards; and (2) ensure that parties demonstrate respect for internationally recognized human rights, as indicated through assessments over a period of at least 10 years."
